{"tid":23930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（賤）台灣男係機場掟死bb狗!","createTime":"2016-12-05T08:56:04.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-05T12:48:47.000Z","uid":29314,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5c6a82e737d4b0fe1adcad2b14a7bc7af00e9eb2","tid":23930,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T08:56:04.000Z","msg":"台灣高雄小港機場，昨日下午4時45分許發生虐狗事件。&hellip;&hellip;一名要搭機前往金門的蘇姓男乘客（41歲），因想託運一隻年僅2個月大的松鼠狗前往金門，但因檢疫問題遭地勤拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n蘇男竟一時氣憤，將<span style=\"color: red;\">裝着小狗的狗籠往地上猛摔</span>，隨即轉身前往搭機，離開前還補踢狗籠一腳，松鼠狗飛上半空撞柱子後重摔在地。<br />\n<br />\n清潔工見狀上前察看，卻驚見松鼠狗吐血死亡。"},{"pid":"46fcb3dde3ca884020430d3930800dd3f2e286ca","tid":23930,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T08:56:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20161205/large/1480867224_e657.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161205%2Flarge%2F1480867224_e657.jpg&h=f8a20364&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a00af3849ca8c4a67ad84bc8c26506b66cec1fad","tid":23930,"uid":25350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:10:12.000Z","msg":"台灣最美的風景是...."},{"pid":"9e093f5be0fa4f42d43f97c0eef7555d49b12323","tid":23930,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:11:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台灣最美的風景是....</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n菜英文"},{"pid":"fc93b8a9578b3f9399ee27dd36df708c2eb92ea6","tid":23930,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:11:34.000Z","msg":"狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e83b8cb897d061f84900e0dde9dd07d912e4e70","tid":23930,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:12:05.000Z","msg":"兩個月大咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a1a21e7684995dd03902e515261650d37289c5d","tid":23930,"uid":30213,"like":0,"di